42
00:03:20.623 --> 00:03:22.120
Give me a second.

43
00:03:22.125 --> 00:03:23.183
Do you need to sit down?

44
00:03:23.188 --> 00:03:24.182
You're gonna pass out.

45
00:03:24.197 --> 00:03:25.970
I'm just... Well
look. wait 'til nap

46
00:03:25.975 --> 00:03:27.430
time and she's screaming for

47
