Hey. look. how lucky.

92
00:05:47.805 --> 00:05:48.987
Actual blueberries.

93
00:05:48.992 --> 00:05:51.115
Ooh. yum.

94
00:05:51.906 --> 00:05:53.657
Hey. so I've been working

95
00:05:53.662 --> 00:05:55.362
