117
00:06:23.966 --> 00:06:25.922
Yes. okay. I'll help.

118
00:06:25.926 --> 00:06:26.881
Thank you.

119
00:06:26.885 --> 00:06:29.387
See you tonight.

120
00:06:39.190 --> 00:06:40.020
I mean. the fact that

121
00:06:40.024 --> 00:06:41.063
