130
00:06:51.952 --> 00:06:52.761
We'd better.

131
00:06:52.766 --> 00:06:54.429
You know. it's piling up.

132
00:06:54.434 --> 00:06:55.535
Between the shelters.

133
00:06:55.539 --> 00:06:56.369
