155
00:07:24.839 --> 00:07:25.753
Wouldn't miss it.

156
00:07:25.758 --> 00:07:27.520
Council Chair Wardell.

157
00:07:48.508 --> 00:07:49.660
Man. I don't know what

158
00:07:49.665 --> 00:07:51.090
