165
00:07:59.317 --> 00:08:00.170
Hey!

166
00:08:02.115 --> 00:08:04.531
Hey! Hey!

167
00:08:04.536 --> 00:08:06.199
Cut it out!

168
00:08:06.359 --> 00:08:08.941
