169
00:08:08.945 --> 00:08:10.903
Put him down!

170
00:08:12.195 --> 00:08:13.338
Stop. stop!

171
00:08:13.343 --> 00:08:14.739
What is wrong with y'all?

172
00:08:14.743 --> 00:08:15.698
He doesn't pay attention!

173
00:08:15.702 --> 00:08:16.532
He almost killed me

174
00:08:16.536 --> 00:08:17.226
