177
00:08:19.206 --> 00:08:21.205
He's drunk. He's drunk!

178
00:08:21.209 --> 00:08:22.038
He's always drunk!

179
00:08:22.042 --> 00:08:22.873
Hey! All right!

180
00:08:22.877 --> 00:08:23.476
We don't have time

181
00:08:23.481 --> 00:08:24.312
