207
00:09:21.602 --> 00:09:24.058
Hey. they have music
there sometimes.

208
00:09:24.062 --> 00:09:26.287
You used to play
the piano. right?

209
00:09:27.440 --> 00:09:29.105
Yeah. sometimes.

210
00:09:29.109 --> 00:09:30.773
In the Nightcar.

211
00:09:30.777 --> 00:09:31.941
Well. maybe if it comes

212
00:09:31.945 --> 00:09:33.991
