213
00:09:38.618 --> 00:09:40.662
Thank you for this.

214
00:10:10.484 --> 00:10:11.605
Welcome. everyone.

215
00:10:11.609 --> 00:10:12.773
to tonight's meeting of

216
00:10:12.777 --> 00:10:13.941
